      <title>多伦多席位失利引发辞职呼声 特鲁多坚持立场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/trudeau-digs-in-after-toronto-seat-loss-sparks-resignation-calls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多明确表示，尽管在多伦多特别选举中失利，使他陷入了职业生涯中最艰难的政治危机，但他仍打算继续留任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/trudeau-digs-in-after-toronto-seat-loss-sparks-resignation-calls</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 18:23:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>辩论后，纽约时报民意调查显示特朗普领先拜登</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/trump-lead-over-biden-grows-in-post-debate-new-york-times-poll</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据《纽约时报》/锡耶纳学院的民意调查，共和党人唐纳德·特朗普在潜在选民中的领先优势已扩大到总统乔·拜登 6 个百分点，这加大了这位陷入困境的民主党现任总统退出竞选的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/trump-lead-over-biden-grows-in-post-debate-new-york-times-poll</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 17:56:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选消息不断升温，华尔街警惕拜登退场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/wall-street-on-alert-for-biden-exit-as-trump-win-trades-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华盛顿关于总统乔·拜登是否放弃竞选连任的激烈辩论正在蔓延到华尔街，交易员们正在将资金转移到美元、美国国债和其他可能受唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫影响的资产上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/wall-street-on-alert-for-biden-exit-as-trump-win-trades-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 17:53:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>白宫承诺向乌克兰提供 23 亿美元武器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/white-house-to-announce-2-3-billion-package-of-arms-for-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据美国官员透露，白宫宣布向乌克兰提供价值 23 亿美元的武器装备，其中包括五角大楼库存的设备以及与洛克希德马丁公司和 RTX 公司签订的防空武器长期合同。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/white-house-to-announce-2-3-billion-package-of-arms-for-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 17:40:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
